er</i> lets you control the wind as it blows a single flower petal around the stages. The petal interacts with various elements in the world, triggering wind turbines or rejuvenating the landscape.</p>\n<p>Rather than focus on traditional design principles of ‘fun’ or challenging gameplay, Chen and Clark instead worked to create a meditative experience they hoped would provoke positive emotions in the player.</p>"], "credit_line_for_label": "", "details": [{"label": "Curatorial section", "display_values": ["The Story of the Moving Image&nbsp;→ Games Lab&nbsp;→ 03. Cluster 3&nbsp;→ GL-03-C01"]}], "stats": {"tap_count": 7839}, "links": [], "creators_primary": [{"id": 1033639, "name": "Sony", "creator_id": 71968, "role": "creator", "role_id": 968, "is_primary": true}, {"id": 1033638, "name": "thatgamecompany", "creator_id": 84333, "role": "creator", "role_id": 968, "is_primary": true}], "creators_other": [], "video_links": [], "media_note": null, "images": [{"id": 17087, "image_file": "https://acmi-public-api.s3.amazonaws.com/image/P180733_G449_flower-listing-thumb-01-psvita-us-05may14.png", "image_file_thumbnail": "https://acmi-public-api.s3.amazonaws.com/image/P180733_G449_flower-listing-thumb-01-psvita-us-05may14.png.1200x1200_q85.png", "image_file_xs": "https://acmi-public-api.s3.amazonaws.com/image/P180733_G449_flower-listing-thumb-01-psvita-us-05may14.png.480x480_q85.png", "image_file_s": "https://acmi-public-api.s3.amazonaws.com/image/P180733_G449_flower-listing-thumb-01-psvita-us-05may14.png.960x960_q85.png", "image_file_m": "https://acmi-public-api.s3.amazonaws.com/image/P180733_G449_flower-listing-thumb-01-psvita-us-05may14.png.1920x1920_q85.png", "image_file_l": "https://acmi-public-api.s3.amazonaws.com/image/P180733_G449_flower-listing-thumb-01-psvita-us-05may14.png.3840x3840_q85.png", "caption": "", "credit_line": "", "alt_text": "", "width": 1422, "height": 800, "access_level": "View anywhere"}, {"id": 17086, "image_file": "https://acmi-public-api.s3.amaz